										<p>Build responsive designs that work perfectly across all devices and screen sizes.</p>
									</div>
								</div>
								<div class="timeline-item">
									<div class="timeline-icon">üß™</div>
									<div class="timeline-content">
										<h4>Testing & Optimization</h4>
										<p>Conduct usability testing and optimize the design for maximum conversion rates.</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="service-features">
							<h3>Design Services</h3>
							<div class="features-grid">
								<div class="feature-item">
									<div class="feature-icon">üì±</div>
									<h4>Responsive Design</h4>
									<p>Mobile-first designs that provide optimal user experience across all devices and screen sizes.</p>
								</div>
								<div class="feature-item">
									<div class="feature-icon">üéØ</div>
